short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Create Instant Google Meet with MeetX

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
MeetX is a powerful browser extension that allows you to effortlessly create Google Meet sessions with just one click. Whether you're organizing a quick meeting or need to connect with others instantly, MeetX makes it easy to generate and share a Google Meet link in seconds.

Key Features:

Instant Google Meet Creation: Create a Google Meet link instantly with a single click.
Retrieve Last Meeting: Quickly access your last meeting link for easy reference or rejoin.
Edit Meeting Name: Update the name of your Google Meet session with ease for better organization.
Simple and Convenient: Save time and streamline your virtual meetings with the simplicity and convenience of MeetX.
With MeetX, managing your Google Meet sessions has never been easier. Save time, stay organized, and focus on what matters mostâ€”your meetings.
